WEBVTT

01:50.190 --> 01:53.930
[Love Between Lines]

01:54.320 --> 01:56.780
[Episode 7]

01:59.000 --> 01:59.840
Ms. Wang,

02:00.760 --> 02:01.820
congratulations,

02:01.950 --> 02:02.710
really.

02:04.120 --> 02:05.000
Thank you.

02:05.640 --> 02:06.950
To be honest with you,

02:07.120 --> 02:09.630
I didn't expect to get married so early.

02:10.000 --> 02:12.330
I was actually afraid of marriage before.

02:14.240 --> 02:15.030
Indeed.

02:15.560 --> 02:18.490
Flash marriage, in particular,
needs more courage.

02:18.630 --> 02:19.590
Flash marriage?

02:20.750 --> 02:22.360
How do you know that?

02:25.680 --> 02:26.400
I...

02:26.670 --> 02:27.640
Keep in touch.

02:27.920 --> 02:29.250
Please stay for a while.

02:29.250 --> 02:30.310
Let me add you on WeChat.

02:30.310 --> 02:30.870
Okay.

02:30.890 --> 02:31.320
Okay.

02:31.870 --> 02:32.310
Okay.

02:32.310 --> 02:32.710
Okay.

02:39.400 --> 02:40.030
Liang,

02:40.370 --> 02:41.400
take care of everyone for me.

02:41.400 --> 02:41.870
Go ahead.

02:41.870 --> 02:42.430
Go ahead. Go ahead.

02:42.430 --> 02:43.090
Okay. Okay.

02:56.710 --> 02:57.280
Congratulations.

02:57.280 --> 02:58.030
Your son married into a good family.

02:58.030 --> 02:59.190
Congratulations.

02:59.870 --> 03:01.000
Thanks to you.

03:01.590 --> 03:02.190
I'm so jealous.

03:02.190 --> 03:02.870
Son!

03:02.870 --> 03:03.150
Yes.

03:03.150 --> 03:03.800
Son!

03:05.150 --> 03:06.080
He's too busy to hear me.

03:06.080 --> 03:06.960
Wait for me.

03:06.980 --> 03:07.770
Okay. Okay.

03:07.800 --> 03:08.730
Qiran.

03:09.150 --> 03:10.150
What were you doing?

03:10.150 --> 03:11.520
You didn't answer when I called you.

03:11.520 --> 03:12.590
Auntie Xu and others are here.

03:12.590 --> 03:13.520
Go and say hello.

03:15.820 --> 03:16.620
Hu Xiu is here.

03:17.520 --> 03:18.150
Hu Xiu?

03:18.579 --> 03:19.820
Why is she here?

03:20.470 --> 03:21.670
Does she know that...

03:23.400 --> 03:23.970
How about this?

03:23.970 --> 03:25.380
Go and attend to the guests.

03:25.380 --> 03:26.380
Leave Hu Xiu to me.

03:26.640 --> 03:28.500
I won't let her ruin your wedding.

04:10.980 --> 04:11.980
Flash marriage?

04:13.070 --> 04:14.630
How do you know that?

04:15.270 --> 04:17.320
But I don't think

04:17.350 --> 04:18.810
it's an accurate description.

04:18.810 --> 04:20.750
We've known each other for over a year.

04:20.750 --> 04:22.390
We dated

04:22.390 --> 04:24.650
for more than half a year
to decide on our marriage.

04:24.650 --> 04:25.530
Half a year?

04:26.190 --> 04:26.830
Yes.

04:27.120 --> 04:27.920
A while back,

04:27.940 --> 04:29.210
he gave up everything in Shanghai

04:29.210 --> 04:30.610
and came to Suzhou for me.

04:30.950 --> 04:32.470
He did really well.

04:32.780 --> 04:35.040
That's why my dad agreed to our marriage.

04:35.220 --> 04:37.290
I told him to arrange the wedding
as soon as possible,

04:37.290 --> 04:39.550
so that my dad wouldn't keep testing him.

04:58.650 --> 05:00.160
Send the tablet and information in the bag

05:00.160 --> 05:03.160
to the conference room
on the third floor of the hotel.

05:07.070 --> 05:09.800
Is he here for the Lyman project?

05:10.750 --> 05:11.520
Hold it.

05:11.960 --> 05:13.440
Don't ruin the business.

05:23.560 --> 05:24.560
Is anyone there?

05:24.700 --> 05:26.700
This door is broken. I can't open it!

05:28.530 --> 05:30.310
[Is Being Inspected and Repaired]

05:32.830 --> 05:33.310
[Mr. Xiao]

05:37.950 --> 05:40.610
You're here
for the design competition's sake?

05:41.110 --> 05:41.720
Yes.

05:42.900 --> 05:45.230
Your studio has already been eliminated.

05:45.500 --> 05:47.360
Letting you rejoin the competition

05:47.360 --> 05:49.360
would be unfair to other companies.

05:50.920 --> 05:52.960
When this island was being developed,

05:52.960 --> 05:54.820
Mr. Wang invited many designers.

05:56.150 --> 05:57.350
But they all refused.

05:58.870 --> 06:00.200
So why did you accept it?

06:01.360 --> 06:03.420
Precisely because they all refused.

06:04.750 --> 06:05.800
In others' eyes,

06:06.370 --> 06:07.770
this was just wasteland.

06:07.930 --> 06:10.060
But the more something is overlooked,

06:11.080 --> 06:13.140
the more it deserves to be redefined.

06:18.150 --> 06:18.830
Mr. Xie.

06:20.990 --> 06:21.640
Mr. Xie?

06:23.210 --> 06:23.920
I'm sorry.

06:25.580 --> 06:28.040
You just reminded me
of someone from my past.

06:28.430 --> 06:30.430
Is that person your friend, Mr. Xie?

06:32.960 --> 06:33.960
I suppose so.

06:47.920 --> 06:49.580
It'll be late if I don't go now.

08:00.390 --> 08:03.790
What does the island project have to do
with the competition?

08:04.070 --> 08:05.530
What are you trying to say?

08:06.250 --> 08:07.810
I want to know your choice—

08:08.560 --> 08:10.020
will you stick to the rules

08:10.280 --> 08:10.890
or choose

08:10.920 --> 08:12.430
a truly valuable design?

08:13.350 --> 08:14.210
All right then.

08:14.350 --> 08:15.440
Show me

08:15.470 --> 08:17.060
what you've got.

08:18.680 --> 08:21.940
Since you're here,
you didn't come empty-handed, did you?

08:22.880 --> 08:24.140
Just a moment, please.

08:33.659 --> 08:34.539
Mr. Xiao.

08:39.820 --> 08:40.890
I'm sorry, Mr. Xiao.

08:40.890 --> 08:41.799
I'm late.

08:49.330 --> 08:50.040
Take a look.

08:55.910 --> 08:56.580
Hu Xiu.

08:57.160 --> 08:58.220
After dawn breaks,

08:58.240 --> 09:00.240
don't think about the past anymore.

09:00.270 --> 09:01.790
Our only goal now

09:02.160 --> 09:04.020
is Lyman's competition project.

09:12.940 --> 09:14.720
Building architecture
is just about winning awards.

09:14.720 --> 09:16.050
You said that yourself?

09:17.340 --> 09:18.170
Yes, I did.

09:20.850 --> 09:22.180
My goal in architecture

09:22.530 --> 09:23.770
does partly involve

09:23.790 --> 09:25.080
impressing the judges

09:25.380 --> 09:26.510
and winning awards.

09:28.010 --> 09:29.810
Every line drawn by an architect

09:30.130 --> 09:30.990
is a statement.

09:31.200 --> 09:32.260
And winning awards

09:32.930 --> 09:35.390
is the best challenge
to break conventions.

09:37.370 --> 09:38.320
I understand that this statement

09:38.320 --> 09:39.560
might cause controversy,

09:39.560 --> 09:42.290
and I respect others'
different interpretations.

09:42.290 --> 09:43.680
But I've never felt

09:44.170 --> 09:45.970
that wanting awards
and creating good architecture

09:45.970 --> 09:47.440
are in any way contradictory.

09:47.440 --> 09:48.440
That's my answer.

09:52.720 --> 09:54.520
As expected from a young person,

09:54.960 --> 09:55.890
ambitious

09:56.170 --> 09:57.010
and driven.

09:57.530 --> 09:59.720
Am I, as an old man, appearing

09:59.720 --> 10:00.920
a bit narrow-minded?

10:12.200 --> 10:12.960
Thank you.

10:14.580 --> 10:15.870
What happened to you?

10:20.320 --> 10:21.250
It's nothing.

10:21.560 --> 10:23.400
I just took a fall.

10:24.600 --> 10:25.290
Where are your shoes?

10:25.290 --> 10:26.620
Where did you lose them?

10:28.290 --> 10:29.170
Forget it.

10:29.290 --> 10:30.550
Don't bother looking.

10:32.360 --> 10:32.960
Let's go.

10:41.600 --> 10:43.200
What are you thinking about?

10:44.900 --> 10:46.780
You knew Mr. Xie was coming today.

10:49.170 --> 10:51.300
I asked Mr. Wang for help to invite him.

10:51.650 --> 10:53.770
I hope we get good news on Monday.

10:58.000 --> 11:01.950
♪ I moved closer to you,
and you moved closer to me ♪

11:02.120 --> 11:05.850
♪ The motionless night began to shimmer ♪

11:06.260 --> 11:10.540
♪ The fireworks bear witness, as if ♪

11:10.870 --> 11:14.100
♪ they're waiting for the words
we want to say ♪

11:14.560 --> 11:17.850
♪ I moved closer to you,
and you moved closer to me ♪

11:19.060 --> 11:24.350
♪ It felt as if two lonely islands
had finally ♪

11:21.650 --> 11:22.770
When we reach the wedding venue later,

11:22.770 --> 11:24.700
I'll borrow a pair of shoes for you.

11:24.990 --> 11:29.600
♪ Getting closer and slipped into
the flow of time together ♪

11:25.370 --> 11:26.050
No need.

11:26.800 --> 11:28.400
I'll wait for you at the dock.

11:30.290 --> 11:30.840
Hu Xiu.

11:31.960 --> 11:33.290
What exactly happened?

11:34.530 --> 11:35.440
I'm just

11:36.320 --> 11:37.080
tired.

11:38.210 --> 11:39.990
Besides, going to the wedding
dressed like this

11:39.990 --> 11:41.330
would be too embarrassing.

11:41.330 --> 11:42.730
Mr. Xie will be there too.

11:44.880 --> 11:46.540
You're overthinking things.

11:47.930 --> 11:49.330
Wait for me near the dock.

11:49.600 --> 11:50.530
Don't go too far.

12:10.490 --> 12:11.920
This is ridiculous.

12:16.180 --> 12:17.150
That person

12:17.170 --> 12:18.320
should be gone by now, right?

12:18.320 --> 12:18.800
Who?

12:19.250 --> 12:20.080
Hu Xiu.

12:20.140 --> 12:22.080
I just saw Qiran's mother following her

12:22.080 --> 12:23.140
to the lounge area.

12:23.340 --> 12:24.220
Hu Xiu is here?

12:24.530 --> 12:25.140
No way.

12:25.640 --> 12:29.240
Zhang Qiran actually invited
his ex-girlfriend to the wedding?

12:47.230 --> 12:47.990
Mr. Xiao.

12:50.060 --> 12:50.590
Let's go.

12:51.530 --> 12:52.320
Where to?

12:54.730 --> 12:55.930
To the wedding venue.

13:00.130 --> 13:01.170
Wang Yue's groom

13:01.290 --> 13:02.740
is the one who broke off the engagement
with you,

13:02.740 --> 13:03.260
right?

13:04.900 --> 13:05.780
How do you know?

13:06.450 --> 13:08.250
I just went to the security room.

13:08.910 --> 13:10.690
The person who locked you
in the lounge area

13:10.690 --> 13:12.150
was Zhang Qiran's mother.

13:17.410 --> 13:17.960
Hu Xiu.

13:19.320 --> 13:21.720
If you're doing this
for the sake of the studio,

13:21.720 --> 13:23.850
I suggest you don't flatter yourself.

13:23.930 --> 13:24.800
My reputation

13:24.800 --> 13:26.320
won't be damaged

13:26.350 --> 13:27.960
just because you don't have
the right shoes.

13:27.960 --> 13:28.650
But if

13:29.890 --> 13:31.530
you've been treated unfairly

13:31.530 --> 13:33.930
and still think
you should swallow your pride,

13:33.930 --> 13:36.790
believing that you're the one
who should hide away,

13:37.850 --> 13:40.110
then just stay here and enjoy the breeze.

14:04.170 --> 14:05.930
Today, we gather here

14:05.930 --> 14:07.480
to witness

14:07.480 --> 14:10.010
this important moment for the couple.

14:10.530 --> 14:11.680
I now declare

14:12.010 --> 14:13.080
that Ms. Wang Yue

14:13.080 --> 14:15.890
and Mr. Zhang Qiran's wedding ceremony

14:16.020 --> 14:18.110
officially begins.

14:30.540 --> 14:32.290
Look how perfect they are together.

14:32.290 --> 14:34.080
Yes, they're a perfect match.

14:34.290 --> 14:35.050
Qiran,

14:35.650 --> 14:37.290
I'm entrusting Wang Yue to you.

14:37.290 --> 14:38.450
Don't worry, Dad.

14:44.370 --> 14:46.010
-Good!
-Good!

14:49.030 --> 14:49.910
Mr. Zhang,

14:50.480 --> 14:53.930
do you take Ms. Wang Yue to be your wife?

14:54.170 --> 14:54.890
I do.

14:56.050 --> 14:57.200
Now, Ms. Wang,

14:57.680 --> 15:01.200
do you take Mr. Zhang Qiran
to be your husband?

15:01.600 --> 15:02.360
I do.

15:09.710 --> 15:12.310
♪ I wanted you to see the light ♪

15:13.980 --> 15:16.350
♪ But you tried to shut it down ♪

15:16.430 --> 15:19.240
♪ That night ♪

15:19.790 --> 15:21.770
Next, the groom and bride,

15:20.530 --> 15:23.160
♪ I know I should be dreaming ♪

15:21.770 --> 15:23.100
please exchange rings.

15:24.870 --> 15:27.150
♪ But I'm still standing here ♪

15:27.470 --> 15:29.910
♪ Trying to take in reality ♪

15:30.410 --> 15:36.470
♪ Just wanna let this storm calm down ♪

15:33.480 --> 15:35.130
We had a small issue just now.

15:35.130 --> 15:37.170
May I ask all the guests in the front rows

15:37.170 --> 15:38.370
to help us look for the ring?

15:37.920 --> 15:40.760
♪ But I can not sleep ♪

15:41.270 --> 15:46.000
♪ Because I'm done pretending ♪

15:44.560 --> 15:45.440
Nothing.

15:46.380 --> 15:48.380
♪ And I ♪

15:48.790 --> 15:50.910
♪ I'm ready, I won't hide ♪

15:50.930 --> 15:53.360
♪ Now it's my turn ♪

15:52.370 --> 15:53.170
I think

15:53.930 --> 15:55.410
the groom's ring has been found.

15:54.390 --> 15:56.860
♪ The reality is boring ♪

15:57.330 --> 16:00.610
♪ Following all the rules ♪

16:01.120 --> 16:03.860
♪ Dreams contend with waking hours ♪

16:06.750 --> 16:09.280
♪ Laid bare ♪

16:09.800 --> 16:13.860
♪ Yesterday all withers now ♪

16:15.190 --> 16:17.360
♪ I hear ♪

16:18.090 --> 16:20.860
♪ The war drums throbbing in my breast ♪

16:20.880 --> 16:27.250
♪ Submerged in tempests of fantasy ♪

16:28.420 --> 16:30.870
♪ Now it's my turn ♪

16:30.890 --> 16:31.420
Mr. Xiao.

16:31.960 --> 16:32.650
Please be seated.

16:32.030 --> 16:34.120
♪ Even if fate ♪

16:34.560 --> 16:35.530
Good things never come easy.

16:34.680 --> 16:37.360
♪ Cycles on and on ♪

16:35.890 --> 16:36.490
Well then,

16:36.520 --> 16:37.650
the bride and groom,

16:37.930 --> 16:40.290
do you have anything you'd like to say
to each other at this moment?

16:38.560 --> 16:42.390
♪ How many tales tomorrow will spawn ♪

16:42.730 --> 16:45.140
♪ I'm free ♪

16:44.600 --> 16:45.290
Yue...

16:45.340 --> 16:48.340
♪ Winner still unknown ♪

16:46.560 --> 16:47.680
Yue

16:48.370 --> 16:49.230
is the best girl

16:49.250 --> 16:52.770
♪ I'll be the one writing my own story ♪

16:49.720 --> 16:51.130
I've ever met.

16:51.770 --> 16:52.930
I feel

16:52.930 --> 16:54.080
that my love...

16:55.410 --> 16:56.440
my love with her

16:57.200 --> 16:58.930
is the greatest fortune

16:59.250 --> 17:00.600
of my life

17:00.840 --> 17:01.890
and also

17:02.010 --> 17:03.340
my greatest happiness.

17:04.369 --> 17:05.089
So,

17:05.369 --> 17:06.520
thank you to all the seniors

17:06.520 --> 17:09.000
and friends for coming here

17:09.170 --> 17:10.369
to witness our union.

17:10.369 --> 17:11.410
I am very happy

17:11.650 --> 17:12.480
and very excited.

17:12.480 --> 17:13.089
Thank you.

17:24.890 --> 17:25.890
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

17:25.890 --> 17:27.240
Thank you. Thank you.

17:29.080 --> 17:30.740
Thanks and congratulations.

17:31.610 --> 17:33.410
Mr. Wang, congratulations.

17:34.000 --> 17:34.680
Having a good time today?

17:34.680 --> 17:35.880
Thank you. Thank you.

17:44.610 --> 17:45.200
Renzi.

17:46.200 --> 17:46.890
Qiran.

17:47.410 --> 17:49.270
I'll take the kids to make a toast.

17:49.370 --> 17:50.010
Alright. Alright.

17:50.010 --> 17:50.400
Dad.

17:51.090 --> 17:51.890
Auntie Zhang.

17:51.930 --> 17:52.720
Okay. Okay.

17:55.440 --> 17:56.040
Mr. Xiao.

17:57.170 --> 17:58.400
Ladies and gentlemen,

17:58.400 --> 18:00.390
thank you all for attending
my daughter's wedding.

18:00.390 --> 18:02.090
I'm here with my daughter and son-in-law

18:02.090 --> 18:03.330
to toast to all of you.

18:03.480 --> 18:04.520
Thank you for coming.

18:04.520 --> 18:04.980
Cheers.

18:05.080 --> 18:06.010
You're too kind.

18:06.850 --> 18:07.440
Here.

18:07.770 --> 18:08.970
Thank you. Thank you.

18:13.810 --> 18:14.410
Mr. Xiao,

18:15.200 --> 18:16.660
hope we can get along well.

18:19.000 --> 18:19.730
Is that okay?

18:27.130 --> 18:28.280
Of course.

18:35.480 --> 18:36.240
Ms. Hu,

18:36.790 --> 18:38.590
what's going on with your shoes?

18:38.890 --> 18:41.350
Why don't I have someone
bring you a new pair?

18:41.810 --> 18:43.000
Yes, Yue,

18:43.170 --> 18:44.520
I think you should have someone

18:44.520 --> 18:46.180
take her to the changing room.

18:46.240 --> 18:47.840
I think the way she's dressed

18:47.880 --> 18:50.330
might not be appropriate
for this occasion.

18:50.330 --> 18:51.170
Yes, indeed.

18:51.370 --> 18:52.130
I'll take you to change your shoes.

18:52.130 --> 18:53.330
It is inappropriate.

18:59.280 --> 19:01.090
So I hope this lady

19:01.200 --> 19:02.800
will return my date's shoes.

19:06.930 --> 19:08.020
S-Shoes?

19:08.170 --> 19:09.170
What shoes?

19:09.820 --> 19:10.750
How would I know?

19:12.290 --> 19:13.240
Mr. Xiao, I think

19:13.340 --> 19:14.810
there might be some misunderstanding.

19:14.810 --> 19:16.000
Whether it's a misunderstanding,

19:16.000 --> 19:17.200
your mother

19:17.370 --> 19:18.410
knows perfectly well.

19:18.410 --> 19:18.810
Well,

19:18.890 --> 19:20.090
what's going on here?

19:20.720 --> 19:21.200
Dad,

19:21.440 --> 19:23.330
I don't really understand

19:23.330 --> 19:25.130
what Mr. Xiao was talking about.

19:25.200 --> 19:27.040
I just checked the security footage.

19:27.040 --> 19:28.040
This lady

19:28.280 --> 19:29.480
locked my date

19:29.480 --> 19:31.280
in the lounge area for no reason,

19:31.520 --> 19:33.520
forcing her to climb out the window.

19:33.720 --> 19:34.610
I'd like to know

19:34.960 --> 19:36.290
what on earth happened.

19:37.720 --> 19:38.570
Is this true?

19:40.930 --> 19:42.330
I didn't do it on purpose.

19:42.520 --> 19:43.930
It's just a lounge area.

19:44.090 --> 19:46.040
How could I know if anyone was inside?

19:46.040 --> 19:48.080
It should be locked if no one's inside.

19:48.080 --> 19:49.540
Are you here for a wedding,

19:50.600 --> 19:52.330
or are you a hotel staff member?

19:54.480 --> 19:55.650
What's exactly going on?

19:55.650 --> 19:57.100
You know Ms. Hu?

19:59.650 --> 20:00.280
Yue.

20:01.260 --> 20:02.260
Actually, Dad...

20:02.440 --> 20:03.850
I was his fiancée

20:06.370 --> 20:08.930
until he suddenly broke up with me
3 months ago.

20:08.930 --> 20:09.610
What?

20:15.400 --> 20:16.570
Three months ago?

20:17.480 --> 20:18.410
No, darling.

20:20.670 --> 20:21.960
When it comes to relationships,

20:21.960 --> 20:23.360
things are never simple.

20:23.410 --> 20:25.090
I never expected that after we split,

20:25.090 --> 20:26.000
I would so quickly meet

20:26.000 --> 20:27.330
the person I truly love.

20:27.370 --> 20:27.810
No.

20:27.960 --> 20:28.720
Mom, Dad,

20:28.780 --> 20:30.380
I really love your daughter.

20:30.650 --> 20:31.440
You don't actually think

20:31.440 --> 20:32.930
that calling your two-timing

20:32.930 --> 20:34.170
a seamless transition
to a new relationship

20:34.170 --> 20:35.770
makes you look noble, do you?

20:36.180 --> 20:38.940
You waited until the engagement day
to break up,

20:38.960 --> 20:41.410
then disappeared without any apology.

20:43.280 --> 20:46.810
Zhang Qiran, how can you
live with yourself being so shameless?

20:47.280 --> 20:48.090
No, Dad.

20:50.480 --> 20:51.000
Yue.

20:52.040 --> 20:53.410
I'm sorry

20:53.650 --> 20:55.310
for disrupting your wedding.

20:56.090 --> 20:57.090
But I'm also grateful

20:57.090 --> 20:58.720
that I came here today.

20:59.480 --> 21:01.240
Heaven helped me see the truth.

21:02.630 --> 21:04.490
I hope you can cut your losses now.

21:09.440 --> 21:10.200
Qiran.

21:14.050 --> 21:14.640
Yue.

21:14.800 --> 21:15.320
Dad.

21:23.120 --> 21:24.470
Zhang Qiran, you jerk!

21:24.720 --> 21:25.890
How dare you lie to me?

21:25.890 --> 21:28.010
You made me the other woman
without me knowing!

21:28.010 --> 21:29.000
Let me explain.

21:29.000 --> 21:30.400
What else is there to say?

21:30.970 --> 21:33.300
Qiran had no feelings for her long ago.

21:33.480 --> 21:34.720
It's just that he was too soft-hearted,

21:34.720 --> 21:36.650
so he kept putting off telling her.

21:59.920 --> 22:01.090
I-I'll handle this myself.

22:01.090 --> 22:01.760
Don't move.

22:26.480 --> 22:27.570
Thank you.

22:38.370 --> 22:39.300
Let me carry you.

22:39.780 --> 22:40.990
No, I...

22:41.020 --> 22:41.740
I...

22:41.920 --> 22:42.570
Get on.

23:01.610 --> 23:02.370
Hold tight.

23:13.850 --> 23:15.170
Will what happened today

23:15.170 --> 23:17.240
affect your relationship

23:17.240 --> 23:18.280
with the client?

23:19.810 --> 23:20.480
Maybe.

23:26.370 --> 23:27.130
Worst case,

23:28.410 --> 23:31.010
I'll design something award-winning
for him.

24:00.170 --> 24:00.890
Where do you live?

24:00.890 --> 24:01.950
I'll take you home.

24:02.850 --> 24:05.200
Just drop me off
at the murder mystery game club.

24:05.200 --> 24:05.930
Thanks.

24:06.570 --> 24:07.440
Your foot is in this condition,

24:07.440 --> 24:09.520
and you still want to play
murder mystery games?

24:09.520 --> 24:11.980
Besides, it's too late
for the last session.

24:28.440 --> 24:30.000
That's my best friend's café.

24:30.000 --> 24:30.960
I live upstairs.

24:31.600 --> 24:34.000
If there's nothing else,
I'll be going now.

24:34.440 --> 24:35.570
You don't look well.

24:39.650 --> 24:41.850
I probably haven't had time
to eat all day.

24:41.850 --> 24:44.050
I'll feel better after I eat something.

24:44.760 --> 24:45.960
What about your foot?

24:46.150 --> 24:47.950
It's much better after resting.

25:41.590 --> 25:44.040
[Opening Hours]

26:00.610 --> 26:01.480
Zhao.

26:02.480 --> 26:03.810
What are you doing here?

26:03.850 --> 26:05.570
Your colleague called me,
saying you had a stomachache

26:05.570 --> 26:06.610
and injured your foot.

26:06.610 --> 26:07.680
Let me see where it is.

26:07.680 --> 26:08.570
Colleague?

26:11.040 --> 26:11.760
Here?

26:12.570 --> 26:13.490
It's nothing.

26:17.850 --> 26:19.040
When I got upstairs

26:19.410 --> 26:20.940
and saw the lights were off,

26:21.130 --> 26:22.240
I thought something else
had happened to you.

26:22.240 --> 26:23.480
You scared me to death.

26:23.480 --> 26:24.810
Speaking of the lights,

26:24.960 --> 26:27.760
do you know the electricity bill
hasn't been paid?

26:27.760 --> 26:30.000
Send me the payment details quickly,

26:30.030 --> 26:31.760
so it'll be easier for me to live here.

26:31.760 --> 26:32.170
Sure.

26:32.170 --> 26:33.530
I'll send them to you later.

26:33.530 --> 26:35.480
I'll make up the medicine with hot water.

26:35.480 --> 26:38.210
It'll warm your stomach
and make you feel better.

26:38.480 --> 26:39.650
Later, you need to tell me

26:39.650 --> 26:41.650
what exactly happened to your foot.

26:48.860 --> 26:51.200
Zhang Qiran is really a piece of work.

26:51.520 --> 26:53.570
Why didn't you curse him out more?

26:53.930 --> 26:55.960
You should have yelled at him

26:55.960 --> 26:58.560
and pointed at his face,
calling him a scumbag.

27:00.100 --> 27:01.820
I actually thought before

27:02.200 --> 27:03.090
that our breakup

27:03.090 --> 27:05.000
might have been partly my fault.

27:06.040 --> 27:07.890
But today I found out

27:08.370 --> 27:11.570
I was just his placeholder
until he found someone better.

27:11.850 --> 27:13.740
So I had nothing more to say.

27:15.440 --> 27:17.280
And the one who should be cursing him out
shouldn't be me;

27:17.280 --> 27:18.480
it should be Ms. Wang.

27:19.000 --> 27:20.800
I could tell from so many details

27:21.000 --> 27:22.810
that she was really looking forward to

27:22.810 --> 27:24.610
and excited about this wedding.

27:25.720 --> 27:28.720
She never expected something like this
would happen.

27:36.850 --> 27:37.440
Xiu.

27:38.130 --> 27:39.260
Think of it this way:

27:39.480 --> 27:40.330
Zhang Qiran

27:40.330 --> 27:42.280
is like what you call in architecture,

27:42.280 --> 27:43.480
a dangerous building.

27:43.480 --> 27:45.000
If you or Ms. Wang

27:45.370 --> 27:46.680
wants to deal with him,

27:46.680 --> 27:48.330
you'd need department approvals,

27:48.330 --> 27:49.170
institutional assessments,

27:49.170 --> 27:50.900
and all sorts of certificates.

27:51.410 --> 27:52.650
When you've lived in a house
for a long time,

27:52.650 --> 27:54.250
you develop feelings for it.

27:54.440 --> 27:56.520
During that long waiting process,

27:56.890 --> 27:58.490
you might soften your heart.

27:58.890 --> 27:59.810
But now,

28:01.330 --> 28:03.440
even heaven can't stand it anymore.

28:03.650 --> 28:04.960
It was afraid falling bricks

28:04.960 --> 28:05.930
and the wind coming in

28:05.930 --> 28:07.060
would make you sick.

28:07.440 --> 28:09.500
So it just demolished it completely.

28:10.480 --> 28:11.570
All you need to do

28:12.040 --> 28:13.760
is rebuild on this land.

28:18.890 --> 28:20.240
How did I not notice

28:20.610 --> 28:22.570
you're so good at comforting people?

28:22.570 --> 28:25.500
No wonder you can come up with 6 names
for your coffee.

28:26.240 --> 28:26.960
Come on,

28:26.960 --> 28:27.890
I came up with 6 names

28:27.890 --> 28:29.490
just so you could choose one.

28:34.830 --> 28:36.180
Is my foot swollen?

28:36.930 --> 28:39.390
I'll get some coffee
to reduce the swelling.

28:39.650 --> 28:41.200
How does coffee reduce swelling?

28:41.200 --> 28:42.130
For a foot soak?

28:42.480 --> 28:43.000
Right.

28:43.200 --> 28:44.400
It works really well.

28:45.200 --> 28:47.240
Why don't we use
your most expensive coffee?

28:47.240 --> 28:48.330
Sure, that works.

28:58.930 --> 28:59.570
Mr. Xiao,

28:59.930 --> 29:00.480
morning.

29:01.330 --> 29:01.960
Morning.

29:04.080 --> 29:04.670
Mr. Xiao.

29:07.520 --> 29:08.480
I have good news.

29:12.280 --> 29:13.000
Everyone,

29:13.520 --> 29:15.320
please pause what you're doing.

29:15.810 --> 29:17.540
I have an announcement to make.

29:17.600 --> 29:19.920
We just received an email from Lyman.

29:20.000 --> 29:21.520
Our competition qualification

29:21.520 --> 29:22.610
has been restored!

29:24.650 --> 29:25.860
Our plan is correct!

29:26.650 --> 29:27.240
It isn't in vain!

29:27.240 --> 29:28.570
Right, it isn't in vain!

29:28.960 --> 29:30.720
-Keep going!
-Keep going!

29:31.350 --> 29:32.110
Let's work!

29:32.360 --> 29:33.000
Alright!

29:33.310 --> 29:33.720
Let's get to work!

29:33.720 --> 29:34.250
Let's go.

29:37.520 --> 29:38.280
Sun,

29:38.460 --> 29:39.860
why isn't Mr. Jiang here?

29:40.570 --> 29:41.430
He's resigned.

29:42.610 --> 29:43.610
That's so sudden.

29:52.200 --> 29:54.090
After the disqualification news came out,

29:54.090 --> 29:56.550
he submitted his resignation
within 2 days.

29:57.340 --> 29:59.000
I thought he was just taking a leave.

29:59.000 --> 30:00.370
Not at all.

30:01.240 --> 30:01.850
That architecture forum

30:01.850 --> 30:03.610
where Mr. Xiao's recording was leaked,

30:03.610 --> 30:05.540
haven't you checked it for a while?

30:06.170 --> 30:07.850
Some comments made me angry.

30:07.960 --> 30:09.960
I haven't checked it for a long time.

30:10.370 --> 30:11.200
These days,

30:11.370 --> 30:13.880
there are suddenly many posts
about Jiang Tianyi,

30:13.880 --> 30:14.760
saying that he is

30:14.760 --> 30:16.680
the mole in Dynamism.

30:17.440 --> 30:18.480
Why would he do that?

30:18.480 --> 30:19.890
I don't know.

30:19.960 --> 30:20.850
But that's not important.

30:20.850 --> 30:21.780
What matters is,

30:22.410 --> 30:23.000
look,

30:23.000 --> 30:25.130
there's this new press release today.

30:30.010 --> 30:32.940
I practice architecture
to win awards and gain fame.

30:33.230 --> 30:35.010
Winning awards gives me more options

30:35.010 --> 30:36.540
to work on better projects.

30:39.810 --> 30:40.850
Think about it. This recording

30:40.850 --> 30:44.050
could only have been released
by the boss himself, right?

30:45.300 --> 30:46.650
So I'm confused.

30:46.940 --> 30:49.200
If the boss has the complete recording
all along,

30:49.200 --> 30:51.000
why wait until now to release it?

30:53.570 --> 30:54.680
Mr. Xiao actually

30:54.850 --> 30:57.450
put his best resources
where they matter most.

30:57.900 --> 30:58.830
What do you mean?

31:05.880 --> 31:07.160
[Didn't they say Dynamism is fighting
for Lyman Group's new project?]

31:09.370 --> 31:10.480
No wonder.

31:10.760 --> 31:11.760
After this recording came out,

31:11.760 --> 31:13.960
Lyman has restored
our competition qualification.

31:13.960 --> 31:15.850
Isn't this just free publicity?

31:16.440 --> 31:17.240
Not just that.

31:19.000 --> 31:20.280
Every step

31:20.650 --> 31:21.580
was calculated.

31:22.280 --> 31:22.850
What?

31:24.270 --> 31:24.860
Nothing.

31:25.650 --> 31:27.090
I even suspect

31:27.090 --> 31:28.330
that those posts by Jiang Tianyi

31:28.330 --> 31:29.990
were all arranged by Mr. Xiao.

31:31.930 --> 31:32.760
Hu Xiu,

31:33.440 --> 31:34.520
from now on,

31:36.240 --> 31:37.640
don't mess with Mr. Xiao.

31:47.300 --> 31:49.100
Their competition eligibility

31:50.410 --> 31:52.010
has actually been restored.

31:53.090 --> 31:53.680
Yes.

31:54.690 --> 31:56.620
Lyman just made the announcement.

31:58.290 --> 31:59.870
There's one more thing, Mr. Pei.

31:59.870 --> 32:02.330
Xiao Zhiyu's reputation has turned around.

32:02.610 --> 32:05.070
After the complete recording was released,

32:05.200 --> 32:06.930
everyone online is talking about it,

32:06.930 --> 32:08.720
and they're optimistic about
his participation in Lyman's competition.

32:08.720 --> 32:09.910
Sun Daqin

32:10.180 --> 32:11.620
repeatedly promised me

32:12.000 --> 32:14.330
that he wouldn't let him
meet with Xie Lin.

32:15.280 --> 32:16.960
It's only been one weekend.

32:19.090 --> 32:20.810
How did he get Xie Lin to agree?

32:23.520 --> 32:24.280
Speak up.

32:25.360 --> 32:26.490
It was my oversight.

32:26.770 --> 32:28.090
I heard from Sun Daqin

32:28.480 --> 32:31.200
that Xie Lin would attend a wedding
on the weekend,

32:31.200 --> 32:33.930
but I didn't expect Xiao Zhiyu
would be there too.

32:34.280 --> 32:36.890
He's quite good at turning things around
in desperate situations.

32:36.890 --> 32:37.680
However,

32:38.090 --> 32:38.810
Dynamism

32:38.810 --> 32:40.200
has been less than 5 years
since its founding.

32:40.200 --> 32:41.400
They lack experience

32:41.410 --> 32:44.030
and might not be able
to handle such a large project.

32:44.030 --> 32:45.310
It's not enough.

32:46.610 --> 32:47.680
What I want

32:48.570 --> 32:49.850
is Dynamism

32:50.570 --> 32:52.830
to have absolutely no chance of winning.

32:59.200 --> 32:59.930
Mr. Xiao.

33:05.570 --> 33:06.370
Um,

33:06.640 --> 33:09.300
here are the documents
you asked me to organize.

33:09.550 --> 33:10.950
Just put them on the desk.

33:17.170 --> 33:18.520
Um, Mr. Xiao.

33:19.570 --> 33:22.570
Was it you who called my friend yesterday?

33:23.380 --> 33:25.410
How did you get my friend's number?

33:26.320 --> 33:27.720
You go in and out every day

33:27.960 --> 33:30.220
and haven't noticed the sign at the door?

33:30.570 --> 33:32.170
It has contact numbers on it.

33:36.440 --> 33:39.370
Did you also buy that medicine?

33:42.330 --> 33:44.170
My friend wants to thank you
for the medicine you bought.

33:44.170 --> 33:45.130
When she came back,

33:45.130 --> 33:47.330
all the pharmacies nearby were closed.

33:47.760 --> 33:49.720
I just hope
your foot injury heals quickly,

33:49.720 --> 33:51.450
so you can get back to work soon.

33:56.850 --> 33:57.370
Hello.

33:57.680 --> 33:58.280
We're from Dynamism.

33:58.280 --> 33:59.680
We're here for a meeting.

33:59.890 --> 34:00.750
Please come in.

34:04.170 --> 34:04.760
Sun,

34:05.430 --> 34:07.030
did you bring the documents?

34:07.960 --> 34:08.600
The car key.

34:08.600 --> 34:10.060
I'll go get the documents.

34:22.370 --> 34:23.440
Jiang Tianyi.

34:24.139 --> 34:25.469
What are you doing here?

34:26.040 --> 34:27.040
None of your business.

34:27.040 --> 34:27.969
Get out of my way.

34:28.730 --> 34:29.980
Jiang Tianyi! Jiang Tianyi.

34:29.980 --> 34:30.710
Calm down.

34:31.159 --> 34:34.080
Whatever it is,
let's sit down and talk it through.

34:34.159 --> 34:35.850
Stop pretending to be nice to me.

34:35.850 --> 34:36.810
Look what's happened to me.

34:36.810 --> 34:38.170
I won't let them get away with this!

34:38.170 --> 34:39.570
Jiang Tianyi, calm down.

34:39.600 --> 34:40.560
Calm down.

34:40.560 --> 34:42.370
Nothing can't be overcome.

34:42.370 --> 34:43.030
Move aside.

34:43.250 --> 34:43.850
I won't.

34:43.850 --> 34:44.780
Get out of my way!

34:44.889 --> 34:45.440
Jiang Tianyi, I...

34:45.440 --> 34:46.040
Move!

34:46.040 --> 34:46.810
Jiang Tianyi!

34:46.810 --> 34:48.040
Let's talk this through, Jiang Tianyi!

34:48.040 --> 34:49.000
Get out of my way! Get out of my way!

34:49.000 --> 34:49.810
Jiang Tianyi!

34:49.810 --> 34:50.560
You!

35:09.770 --> 35:11.120
This is a public place,

35:11.260 --> 35:12.590
and you dare hit a woman?

35:12.810 --> 35:14.010
Take him to security.

35:14.270 --> 35:15.310
Move.

35:18.690 --> 35:19.440
Are you okay?

35:19.730 --> 35:20.440
Thank you.

35:23.200 --> 35:25.800
Could you press the first floor for me?
Thanks.

35:34.890 --> 35:36.210
It seems the security in this building

35:36.210 --> 35:37.370
needs improvement.

35:37.460 --> 35:38.480
Did he scare you?

35:38.770 --> 35:39.440
I'm fine.

35:41.540 --> 35:42.910
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

35:42.930 --> 35:44.530
It was really our oversight.

35:45.110 --> 35:45.660
It's okay.

35:45.660 --> 35:46.460
You can go now.

35:49.600 --> 35:50.800
Do you work for Lyman?

35:51.560 --> 35:52.210
No.

35:52.240 --> 35:52.640
I am

35:52.640 --> 35:53.120
an assistant designer

35:53.120 --> 35:54.210
from Dynamism.

35:54.450 --> 35:55.710
I'm here for a meeting.

35:57.810 --> 35:58.440
Perfect.

35:58.440 --> 35:59.900
I'm here for a meeting too.

35:59.930 --> 36:01.130
Let's go up together.

36:02.480 --> 36:03.160
Thank you.

36:18.330 --> 36:19.890
They are currently
the strongest competitors

36:19.890 --> 36:21.160
for our project.

36:22.690 --> 36:24.210
I've called you all here today

36:24.210 --> 36:26.210
mainly to discuss further

36:26.210 --> 36:29.250
some requirements
for the later stages of this project.

36:29.250 --> 36:30.960
Feel free to ask any questions.

36:30.960 --> 36:31.560
Mr. Xie.

36:38.440 --> 36:39.040
Mr. Xiao.

36:45.080 --> 36:47.480
Keeping people waiting isn't a good habit.

36:49.870 --> 36:51.600
I'll be more careful next time.

36:52.120 --> 36:52.650
Let's go.

36:56.810 --> 36:57.410
No rush.

37:04.780 --> 37:05.930
Sorry, I'm late.

37:06.560 --> 37:07.210
Uncle Xie,

37:07.330 --> 37:08.080
sorry to keep you waiting.

37:08.080 --> 37:09.810
It's fine. We just got here too.

37:09.910 --> 37:11.110
Introduce yourself.

37:11.250 --> 37:12.370
I'm Pei Zhen from Zhuling. Hello.

37:12.370 --> 37:12.890
Hello.

37:13.120 --> 37:13.640
Hello.

37:16.610 --> 37:18.740
Why were you with Mr. Pei from Zhuling?

37:20.560 --> 37:21.210
Mr. Pei?

37:22.750 --> 37:23.950
The one with glasses?

37:25.850 --> 37:26.730
I don't know.

37:26.730 --> 37:28.190
I just met him downstairs.

37:29.410 --> 37:31.480
I just realized he's from Zhuling.

37:31.730 --> 37:32.960
From Zhuling?

37:33.310 --> 37:34.830
He's the heir to Zhuling.

37:38.490 --> 37:39.480
You guys go ahead first.

37:39.480 --> 37:40.540
I'll be right back.

37:40.550 --> 37:43.750
[Lyman Group]

37:43.700 --> 37:46.100
Mr. Xiao,
hope we can learn from each other.

37:46.480 --> 37:47.640
Likewise.

37:48.370 --> 37:49.810
Mr. Xiao, you're so talented.

37:49.810 --> 37:51.040
I'm honored

37:51.160 --> 37:52.290
to meet you again.

38:13.120 --> 38:14.160
Since everyone is here,

38:14.160 --> 38:15.040
let's begin.

38:28.080 --> 38:29.850
Let's start with Zheng,

38:29.850 --> 38:31.850
who will brief you on the situation.

38:37.250 --> 38:39.330
As emphasized in the presentation,

38:39.960 --> 38:42.440
our 3 principles for the design plan

38:42.690 --> 38:43.730
are human-centered,

38:43.730 --> 38:44.640
sustainable,

38:44.930 --> 38:45.730
and feasible.

38:46.730 --> 38:47.990
What we're looking for

38:48.040 --> 38:49.480
is not just a design plan,

38:49.890 --> 38:52.810
but a spatial solution
that can carry the city's memories

38:52.810 --> 38:55.480
and meet the needs of future living.

38:55.890 --> 38:56.490
Thank you.

38:59.020 --> 39:00.150
Alright, everyone.

39:00.600 --> 39:02.200
That's the basic situation.

39:02.480 --> 39:03.410
I look forward to

39:03.960 --> 39:05.250
all of you designers

39:05.560 --> 39:07.000
using your creativity

39:07.210 --> 39:08.740
to inject into this project

39:09.120 --> 39:10.730
a brilliant soul.

39:15.690 --> 39:16.770
Today's meeting

39:16.770 --> 39:17.690
is over.

39:18.210 --> 39:19.190
Thank you all for your hard work.

39:19.190 --> 39:20.320
Meeting adjourned.

39:24.560 --> 39:25.490
Wait, everyone.

39:26.730 --> 39:28.190
I need you to fill this out.

39:34.690 --> 39:35.480
Ms. Hu,

39:36.000 --> 39:37.000
see you next time.

39:44.410 --> 39:45.410
When I came back,

39:45.410 --> 39:46.850
I ran into Jiang Tianyi.

39:46.850 --> 39:48.370
He tried to force his way in
and cause trouble.

39:48.370 --> 39:49.410
I couldn't stop him.

39:49.410 --> 39:51.210
Thankfully, Mr. Pei helped out.

40:26.000 --> 40:27.210
If you want a meeting,

40:27.400 --> 40:28.900
just make an appointment
with my assistant.

40:28.900 --> 40:30.080
It's inappropriate

40:30.080 --> 40:31.480
to show up here suddenly.

40:33.230 --> 40:34.730
I don't like those

40:35.160 --> 40:36.560
who think they are smart.

40:38.250 --> 40:38.810
Mr. Pei.

40:43.040 --> 40:43.600
Mr. Pei.

40:43.900 --> 40:45.700
You didn't reply to my messages.

40:45.810 --> 40:46.890
I could only go to Zhuling to find you,

40:46.890 --> 40:48.330
but they didn't let me in.

40:49.640 --> 40:51.370
I had no choice.

40:51.870 --> 40:53.640
I've done what you asked me to do.

40:53.640 --> 40:54.810
We had a deal.

40:55.120 --> 40:57.330
You promised me
the position of Zhuling's design director.

40:57.330 --> 40:58.880
You were not helping me.

41:00.310 --> 41:02.250
It's you who don't accept Xiao Zhiyu.

41:02.250 --> 41:03.910
You wanted to vent your anger.

41:04.280 --> 41:05.880
I just took the opportunity.

41:06.330 --> 41:06.850
I...

41:07.690 --> 41:09.330
After the recording was exposed,

41:09.330 --> 41:10.730
you resigned very soon.

41:11.810 --> 41:12.810
Isn't that right?

41:13.890 --> 41:14.640
Yes.

41:15.120 --> 41:16.520
I was a little impatient.

41:17.450 --> 41:19.290
Should I wait for them to catch me,
Mr. Pei?

41:19.290 --> 41:20.890
I don't ask for anything else.

41:20.890 --> 41:21.810
All I ask is to let me

41:21.810 --> 41:23.560
be a regular staff member at Zhuling.

41:23.560 --> 41:25.760
This decision is a piece of cake for you.

41:27.250 --> 41:28.480
How will others think of me

41:28.480 --> 41:29.600
if I let you join Zhuling?

41:29.600 --> 41:30.600
I don't care!

41:30.730 --> 41:31.890
If I have no choice,

41:32.040 --> 41:33.700
I can't control what I'll say!

41:46.890 --> 41:47.730
Mr. Pei,

41:48.810 --> 41:50.210
I only want one way out.

41:51.040 --> 41:52.640
I beg you.

41:53.270 --> 41:55.080
I'm already on the blacklist
of the industry,

41:55.080 --> 41:55.890
and my reputation is ruined.

41:55.890 --> 41:57.440
I can't find a job at all.

41:58.810 --> 41:59.640
Or...

42:00.450 --> 42:01.210
Or should I

42:01.210 --> 42:02.850
change my name, Mr. Pei?

42:11.040 --> 42:12.410
Change your name?

42:13.770 --> 42:15.250
It's really pathetic.

42:17.390 --> 42:18.810
Your brother has changed his name.

42:18.810 --> 42:20.120
He took after the auntie's surname,

42:20.120 --> 42:21.180
called Xiao Zhiyu.

42:22.000 --> 42:23.480
From now on,

42:23.620 --> 42:25.540
you can't call him by his original name.
